title: Warriors x Pokemon
body:
I bet many of you have watched Pokemon anime series. And I bet many of you remember its opening song. So check this out -- my friend remade the Warriors video with Pokemon music and it fits really well.
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TiEdiz6bcTg

replies.body: I just... this isn't even edited, is it? This fits TOO well, it has to be intentional. Beautiful.

Fits fairly well.

Especially at the start and the first lightning bit.
Speechless... this show has sooo many memories too :')
Haha, at 0:58 it looks like he's saying "Gotta catch 'em all!"
